css:
@namespace url(http://www.mozilla.org/keymaster/gatekeeper/there.is.only.xul);

/* There are five items below that have had their height changed in code... but they only go to
visibly effect the height of one thing... the calendar/task toolbar (only visible under 
calendar/task tabs). You can't just change the height of the toolbar itself, you also have to 
change the height of some of the elements in the toolbar. The first two items are the innermost 
items, the second pair of items contain the innermost items, and the last items "#calendar-
toolbar-deck" is the actual (ie, largest) item we are trying to change. 

REMEMBER: to right-click>CUSTOMIZE the CALENDAR/TASK-TOOLBARS (by clicking on both said 
toolbar(S), and not on the other toolbars) first, and change icon size to small for optimal 
results). */

/* location of items in DOM tree: */
/* #document>window>hbox>tabmail>xul:tabbox>tabpanels>vbox>deck>toolbox:calendar-toolbar-deck */


#calendar-toolbar2
{
    max-height: 15px !important;
    height: 10px !important;
}

#task-toolbar2
{
    max-height: 15px !important;
    height: 10px !important;
}


#calendar-toolbox
{
    max-height: 15px !important;
    height: 10px !important;
}

#task-toolbox
{
    max-height: 15px !important;
    height: 10px !important;
}


#calendar-toolbar-deck
{
    max-height: 20px !important;
    height: 18px !important;
 /* border-bottom: 1px solid #0000FF !important; */
}
